dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line): Outagamie County, Wisconsin, 2020
dct_alternativeTitle_sm: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Outagamie County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Outagamie_Hydro_2020_Line' and 'Outagamie_Hydro_2020_Poly'.Line: [This is a line feature class identifying the location of all non-navigable and navigable water within Outagamie County. It is a county-wide file including all USGS designated navigable waterways and all non-navigable waterways.]Poly: [This is a polygon feature class that corresponds with navigable streams within Outagamie County. This feature class represents the larger areas of the Navigable Streams.]
